Congress has passed the bill

24:27.250 --> 24:30.240
that approves our deal

24:27.250 --> 24:30.240
with our Russian partners.

24:30.250 --> 24:32.100
This should nearly

24:30.250 --> 24:32.100
double our capacity

24:32.110 --> 24:34.210
in the next five years.

24:34.220 --> 24:35.250
But I'm not gonna lie--

24:35.250 --> 24:39.030
it's not good news

24:35.250 --> 24:39.030
for everyone here.

24:39.040 --> 24:41.210
I'm afraid I have some

24:39.040 --> 24:41.210
personnel changes to announce.

24:41.220 --> 24:44.210
Several members of the senior

24:41.220 --> 24:44.210
staff will be staying on

24:44.220 --> 24:47.040
but all level one, two,

24:44.220 --> 24:47.040
and three derrickmen,

24:47.050 --> 24:51.040
motormen, and roughnecks

24:47.050 --> 24:51.040
will be replaced--

24:51.050 --> 24:53.000
effective immediately.

24:53.000 --> 24:54.000
- Fuck you talking about?

24:55.210 --> 24:56.280
- Starting tomorrow morning

24:57.000 --> 24:59.160
a Russian crew

24:57.000 --> 24:59.160
will be taking over.

25:01.100 --> 25:03.080
Now, we will do

25:01.100 --> 25:03.080
everything we can

25:03.090 --> 25:06.080
to facilitate transfers

25:03.090 --> 25:06.080
to another rig.

25:06.090 --> 25:08.150
Unfortunately, at this time

25:06.090 --> 25:08.150
there are no reassignments.

25:08.160 --> 25:09.240
- Hey, keepin' your job, huh?

25:09.250 --> 25:10.190
- And I understand

25:09.250 --> 25:10.190
this is difficult...

25:10.200 --> 25:13.000
- Keepin' your job?

25:13.000 --> 25:15.010
-Your severance checks will be

25:13.000 --> 25:15.010
issued upon arrival in Seattle.

25:15.020 --> 25:16.280
Now, I understand

25:15.020 --> 25:16.280
there's anger...

25:44.110 --> 25:45.250
- Yo.

